strava-activity-year-review

Series of R scripts which takes a Strava user’s activity history data file and outputs a data visualisation summarising the past year

Download your Strava activity data

In order to run the code in this repository, a Strava activity file is required. This can be retrieved through a bulk data export from Strava, as detailed in the following guide: https://support.strava.com/hc/en-us/articles/216918437-Exporting-your-Data-and-Bulk-Export

This will return a zip file containing a .csv file titled ‘activities’.
